1. *Dodjavola* ti sve, ne znam zašto se uopšte trudiš. (To hell with everything, I don't know why you even bother.)
2. Znao sam da će se *dodjavoliti* stvari ako ne budemo pazili. (I knew things would go to hell if we didn't be careful.)
3. Šta je *dodjavola* s tobom, zašto si tako nervozan? (What the hell is wrong with you, why are you so nervous?)
4. Pusti me *dodjavola*, ne mogu sada da pričam. (Leave me the hell alone, I can't talk right now.)
5. *Dodjavola* ovaj račun, ovo je skupo. (To hell with this bill, this is expensive.)
6. Ne razumem *dodjavola* o čemu pričaš. (I don't understand a damn thing you're talking about.)
7. Nema šanse da to uradim *dodjavola*. (There's no way in hell I'm doing that.)
8. *Dodjavola*! Zaboravio sam ključeve u kući. (Damn it! I forgot my keys at home.)